  <shortDescription>News Aggregation Library for Java</shortDescription>

  <description>
    The Informa RSS Library provides a convenient Java API for handling news
    channels and metadata about them. Different syntax formats (like RSS
    0.91 and 1.0 RDF, Atom 0.3 and 1.0) for channels are supported. In addition a parser for
    reading in channel information descriptions (OPML) is provided.
  </description>

